入住的时候，超级nice，因为带了小朋友，小朋友早班飞机很累，想提早入住，给了我们一间不错的房间，送了月饼送了早餐券送了很多欧舒丹洗漱用品，还有小玩具，也是这里有售卖的。
然后服务超级棒。
南航旗下，也会看到其他航空公司工作人员入住。', '2024-01-01', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'', ''客房服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234i12000cud57bi6563_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231q12000cud4oviF38B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230l12000cud3fw14F59_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232v12000cucyv1a9880_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234612000cud562l4EBF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235212000cud562nEEC7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231w12000cud3il498D8_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232d12000cud087o4568_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232t12000cud45573D0D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '有多少人跟我一样认为，里面的人员和服务员多么崇洋媚外？', '有多少人跟我一样认为，里面的人员和服务员多么崇洋媚外？', '2024-02-19', 4, '[''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231l12000d8t3p02B8F2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店非常的不错，酒店大堂很豪华，服务也很不错，特别是大堂的whaley服务不错', '酒店非常的不错，酒店大堂很豪华，服务也很不错，特别是大堂的whaley服务不错', '2024-07-27', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232g12000ewz58g2BAAA_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232p12000ewz7mgdDBB6_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230f12000ewz9f7i5C02_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233m12000ewyy6ho2B45_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234p12000ewz0cafD739_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235d12000ewzazyx7FB2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236912000ewz1jqh1F73_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233112000ewz7f4oBFE7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235r12000ewyvnrjA676_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '带宝宝出行  酒店房间中规中矩  就是隔音太差  旁边房间的关门声 都听的一清二', '带宝宝出行  酒店房间中规中矩  就是隔音太差  旁边房间的关门声 都听的一清二楚而且声音不小  
