对于老广有一定情怀的，除了白天鹅，花园酒店是一个非常值得推荐的打卡酒店～', '2023-09-03', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''餐饮设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230u12000c28svkb41DB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232112000c28xkvh0A6D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236g12000c28wf7bC04A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236f12000c291796E6E0_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231p12000c293wuuC574_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '抓住暑假的尾巴，来到传说中的花园酒店，住店体验非常的好！环境好靓，食品出品干净、', '抓住暑假的尾巴，来到传说中的花园酒店，住店体验非常的好！环境好靓，食品出品干净、精致、味道好！期待下次再来～', '2023-08-28', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''餐饮设施'', ''卫生状况'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230l12000c0qffzi5A1A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230a12000c0qflc8BD56_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234z12000c0qfnq549BF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234112000c0qfqksF293_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235s12000c0qfnm4C40A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '服务到位，清静卫生', '服务到位，清静卫生', '2023-12-07', 4, '[''客房服务'', ''卫生状况'', ''安静程度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233h12000coy04svA6C1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '昨天入住广州花园酒店，给我不一样的感受，接待我们的是Viria和Ariel两位美', '昨天入住广州花园酒店，给我不一样的感受，接待我们的是Viria和Ariel两位美女，她们周到的介绍，细心的服务，让我们宾至如归，她们友好耐心的服务和美美的气质让我们感到花园的服务员是有良好素质和优质服意识的，从此可看到酒店的管理不错，再加上有历史的优美环境，干净整洁的房间，我们马上决定在这住9晚，续订了。很开心。', '2023-08-17', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'', ''卫生状况'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234712000bxpc4b1230F_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '广州老字号酒店，地理位置非常好，地铁口出来100米，环境好，服务很好，前台办理员', '广州老字号酒店，地理位置非常好，地铁口出来100米，环境好，服务很好，前台办理员Niki很漂亮的小姐姐，给我们升级了一个套房，真的是太好了', '2024-05-10', 5, '[''交通便利性'', ''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231612000dxxmlr7C596_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233512000dxxle7u17A1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235712000dxxmq4v2B17_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230s12000dxxminiEFF3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '原来广州花园酒店也是出自顶尖的华裔建筑大师贝聿铭之手，感觉好几个中欧航空公司的空', '原来广州花园酒店也是出自顶尖的华裔建筑大师贝聿铭之手，感觉好几个中欧航空公司的空乘都是专门入住花园酒店的。

?环境亮点：地铁站上来即刻就到酒店 ～ 一进入酒店大厅，你就会为这里设计上深深蕴含的中国传统文化特色而震惊！大堂是大跨度无柱设计、富丽堂皇！正对着的是150平方米的红楼梦《大观园》金箔壁画～ 旁边就是18米双瀑布美景餐厅，在这里用早餐还是蛮心旷神怡的～ 

??房型服务：这次预定的是花园大床房，从房间内的落地玻璃窗就可直接眺望到瀑布，繁华的市区也能有一丝绿意盎然～ 室内的大浴缸令人眼前一亮。不过两天下来并没有专门去泡澡，因为酒店内的桑拿更是给力哦！

??设施齐全：个人原因总是喜欢体验各酒店的泳池和桑拿浴室，而广州也许因为国际客户特别多，因此连桑拿房都分了干湿蒸，也有冰凉的0度冰水给大家冷热交替！ 很多4星酒店这个部分都被搁置不被重视，但花园酒店令人惊喜！

??周边玩乐：酒店里现在有一个广州酒店博物馆～ 看了实在唏嘘。原来1996年，广州花园酒店给员工的服装费就有1600rmb，果然差距好大！花园酒店里还有好几家米其林星级餐厅！中餐、西餐各占2个席位！广州泰安门勇夺广州米其林二星！3楼桃园馆更是以地道粤菜蝉联米其林餐盘奖！可惜这次来没有机会了，下次必须泰安门走起！', '2023-07-08', 5, '[''公共设施'', ''交通便利性'', ''餐饮设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0202e12000blp4n1l96C1_W_350_350_R5_Q70.jpg?proc=autoorient\", \"https://pages.c-ctrip.com/hotels/IBU/online/play-icon.png\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233012000blohrj364AC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234o12000bloorduFFC1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235f12000blohdun531C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232v12000blone3a08CD_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230c12000blom68t8254_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231q12000blook9fAFC4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231y12000bloipox7EA4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '六一老婆生日，因为唔系假日，出唔捣外，所以就拣花园酒店住返晚，贪佢离公司同学校近', '六一老婆生日，因为唔系假日，出唔捣外，所以就拣花园酒店住返晚，贪佢离公司同学校近，就脚。第二次入住喇，老婆对安排好满意。感谢大堂既靓女RAIN，送左份好靓既美颜用品手信，啱晒老婆用。不足：泳池D水有浊。', '2023-06-02', 5, '[''周边配套'', ''前台服务'', ''公共设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232112000bcaotxyBE4C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233f12000bcaktxt1DC5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230312000bcai2si9598_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232s12000bcag9oyFE0C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230t12000bcaiqyl3896_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234r12000bcapltlE9B3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236512000bcajt2u6545_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231312000bcakih53455_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235012000bcaky05087D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '房间设施非常好??', '房间设施非常好??', '2023-11-24', 5, '[''房间设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233v12000cmp9b2oB6F8_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '入住花园酒店是个巧合，航司通知停飞改签至第二天，临时找的酒店。第一眼的印象非常好', '入住花园酒店是个巧合，航司通知停飞改签至第二天，临时找的酒店。第一眼的印象非常好，大堂的布置是歌剧魅影，我们是看完歌剧后入住的，孩子看到后兴奋的不得了。前台Mancy给办的入住，给我们升级了套房，还送了我们欢迎花朵。服务周到细心，知道我们第一次入住给我们介绍了四楼的博物馆和油画展。办理手续非常顺利，动作娴熟，没有等待很久也是直接拿的房。广州玩了几天，下午下雨就直接去观展，还在酒店用了晚膳，体验感很不错，以后会是我再来广州首选的酒店。', '2023-08-02', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'', ''退房/入住效率'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231h12000bt9ye2fE4F6_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235n12000bt9yr154D91_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235712000bt9v1xuF640_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236812000bt9x4cj4555_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236512000bta2u71141B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234w12000bt9tkq93891_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235s12000bt9tkqb2175_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234812000bt9vkdr98EB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234c12000bta2uzpCEC9_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '极具岭南特色的后花园景致和荔湾亭美食 值得再来 也是第一次游广州的最佳之选', '极具岭南特色的后花园景致和荔湾亭美食 值得再来 也是第一次游广州的最佳之选', '2023-09-03', 5, '[''周边配套'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236f12000c26pct078A6_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235h12000c26h7j76FBF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236c12000c26ksx56983_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230u12000c26lta729E3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234212000c26pembC412_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231v12000c26nkwo1F5B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236b12000c26i9ilB6FD_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233912000c26o8w3377E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235c12000c26fmud416E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '办理入住时间比较长，排队地方设置不明显导致有人插队。早餐觉得不如其他五星，房间也', '办理入住时间比较长，排队地方设置不明显导致有人插队。早餐觉得不如其他五星，房间也的确有些年头。就住个情怀打个卡吧，五星好评。', '2023-08-06', 5, '[''退房/入住效率'', ''餐饮设施'', ''房间设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236u12000bufnot49F6E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233m12000bufqgpj71BF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232r12000bufpnma82CF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235f12000bufmxg6C764_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234c12000bufj9td6255_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230y12000bufnfsu46BA_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店很多外宾，上车下车无人帮拿行李，完全感受不到白金五星酒店的服务，略有失望', '酒店很多外宾，上车下车无人帮拿行李，完全感受不到白金五星酒店的服务，略有失望', '2023-09-20', 3, '[''前台服务'', ''客房服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236f12000c6zqmh2AE36_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234712000c6zo4su6EC3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '我们14点到的，但是要两个小时以后才能办入住，一般酒店都会免费升房，但是酒店告诉', '我们14点到的，但是要两个小时以后才能办入住，一般酒店都会免费升房，但是酒店告诉我们如果想要立即入住的话需要自己加钱才能升房哦！也许是周末人比较多吧！价钱比我后面住的喜来登贵，但是总体来说环境，设施，设计，服务等都要改进！', '2023-06-19', 5, '[''退房/入住效率'', ''性价比'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231o12000bg3eq040670_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231r12000bg38y7l80BD_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '房间虽然不是很新也不大，两个人住的还是挺舒适的', '房间虽然不是很新也不大，两个人住的还是挺舒适的
住这里附加值非常高，后花园和博物馆值得带小孩打卡
不用出酒店就能吃到好吃的下午茶
来广州的第一天愉快的吃吃喝喝太合适了', '2023-07-06', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''公共设施'', ''餐饮设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235s12000bl1s6x57DEC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235v12000bl0dqs1DA00_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231x12000bl1qql47152_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232k12000bl1amuk13D2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235s12000bl0w1xk784E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234f12000bl0ivcnE7F1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234412000bl1utpbB002_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0237212000bl1toqyCC06_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235m12000bl0fdg695F7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '不愧是花园酒店，自带的花园超级漂亮，餐饮也很出色，服务热情。', '不愧是花园酒店，自带的花园超级漂亮，餐饮也很出色，服务热情。', '2023-10-03', 5, '[''餐饮设施'', ''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235s12000cbeqw7c6F2E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233112000cbeqgh0843A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '服务非常好，不愧是老牌五星酒店。', '服务非常好，不愧是老牌五星酒店。', '2023-11-01', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236912000chqj4vb7C32_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235l12000chqb842F8E0_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232912000chq5rnlA2A9_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '房间宽敞舒适，设施完备齐全，服务温馨周到，尤其是客房服务中心小刘姑娘真诚热情、细', '房间宽敞舒适，设施完备齐全，服务温馨周到，尤其是客房服务中心小刘姑娘真诚热情、细致入微，必须点赞??', '2025-03-27', 5, '[''房间设施'', ''客房服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232h12000jcrmy650DA3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.png\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233y12000jcro9s21AEE_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.png\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '服务有求必应，交通方便，动静脉分流合理，一楼早晚自助餐品种还行。建议大楼外玻璃清', '服务有求必应，交通方便，动静脉分流合理，一楼早晚自助餐品种还行。建议大楼外玻璃清洗干净，看外面景色模糊。', '2023-08-20', 4, '[''前台服务'', ''交通便利性'', ''餐饮设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235o12000byiwdbg4F84_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230412000byj0s2w810D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231h12000byiw5y04BBC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236j12000byj93936A11_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '第一次来广州，在选入住酒店的时候对比了好多酒店选的花园酒店，酒店一级棒，大堂恢宏', '第一次来广州，在选入住酒店的时候对比了好多酒店选的花园酒店，酒店一级棒，大堂恢宏气派，酒店特别有自己的文化和特色，房间很漂亮整洁，服务人员特别热情周到，办理入住的小姐姐贴心的给我们送了鲜花，还推荐我们参观酒店的博物馆和后花园等网红打卡地，参观了一圈酒店晚上我们还在瀑布餐厅享受了一顿丰盛的自助餐，退房时候大堂的小美女帮我们办理了快速退房还送我们宝格丽的洗护套装，非常奈斯。下次来广州首选花园酒店', '2023-07-10', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'', ''退房/入住效率'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0202312000bmffi4m7D1D_W_350_350_R5_Q70.jpg?proc=autoorient\", \"https://pages.c-ctrip.com/hotels/IBU/online/play-icon.png\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230d12000bmf4zjj5A88_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231f12000bmfdsm0B57B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235n12000bmf5ktuB681_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店环境十分好，后花园瀑布值得一逛。但房间设施有些老旧，玻璃窗全是灰，淋浴和厕所', '酒店环境十分好，后花园瀑布值得一逛。但房间设施有些老旧，玻璃窗全是灰，淋浴和厕所共用一扇移门，推拉不方便，很费劲。洗手池台面也不太干净。', '2023-07-25', 4, '[''房间设施'', ''卫生状况'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235v12000bqx26ct1D1E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234z12000bqx52d099EC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '设施虽然有点儿旧，但是胜在环境好，服务好，食物新鲜，交通非常安全便利，后花园很美', '设施虽然有点儿旧，但是胜在环境好，服务好，食物新鲜，交通非常安全便利，后花园很美，瀑布漂亮，鱼很大。', '2023-08-23', 4, '[''交通便利性'', ''整体满意度'', ''餐饮设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234212000bzhuyy19E23_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234e12000bzht2ql18F1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '父亲节给父母订的酒店，家住广州的老人家花园酒店对他们来说再熟悉不过了，酒店很贴心', '父亲节给父母订的酒店，家住广州的老人家花园酒店对他们来说再熟悉不过了，酒店很贴心的升级了套房，入住用餐的过程中都给予特别关照，父母对此次体验非常满意，充分体现广州老牌五星级的服务水平????', '2023-06-17', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'', ''餐饮设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0204j12000bfs6h1s70FE_W_350_350_R5_Q70.jpg?proc=autoorient\", \"https://pages.c-ctrip.com/hotels/IBU/online/play-icon.png\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236r12000bfrrimaB9CB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '花园酒店装饰富丽堂皇，美轮美奂。酒店分酒店大楼和花园大厦两座Y型大楼。前台服务很', '花园酒店装饰富丽堂皇，美轮美奂。酒店分酒店大楼和花园大厦两座Y型大楼。前台服务很 nice,betty joyce 两人一起接待，感觉宾至如归。', '2023-07-17', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232y12000boj1bun08CB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235z12000boj1fedF9E1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232z12000boj1h452699_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '服务和环境一流水平，不愧为五星级酒店。', '服务和环境一流水平，不愧为五星级酒店。', '2023-10-23', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234v12000cfsmbb119A3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236a12000cfslnzgC538_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231212000cfsmero2F99_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236v12000cfsm3zrB164_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '挺好，送了小点心，结婚纪念日还送了小布置，美中不足泳池维修，没玩上水', '挺好，送了小点心，结婚纪念日还送了小布置，美中不足泳池维修，没玩上水', '2023-09-20', 5, '[''客房服务'', ''公共设施'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232w12000c6xjzou1C7E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '飞机延误，到酒店已凌晨，酒店接待认真负责，还给我们房间升了级，非常满意', '飞机延误，到酒店已凌晨，酒店接待认真负责，还给我们房间升了级，非常满意', '2023-09-17', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233d12000c60yftm3D9F_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235f12000c60zowkAE6F_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230w12000c613uw4BF5D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店环境很温馨、客服服务态度特别好、酒店空间很大、设备设施齐全、房间收拾打扫得一', '酒店环境很温馨、客服服务态度特别好、酒店空间很大、设备设施齐全、房间收拾打扫得一尘不染、而且酒店所处位置地段出行方便、很适合商务旅行', '2023-07-29', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'', ''交通便利性'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236712000bs0kfj097C7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233j12000bs0lux4E78B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232w12000bs0lrr1960B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '每次出差来广州都是入住这家酒店、环境好出行方便地铁淘金站就在酒店旁边……', '每次出差来广州都是入住这家酒店、环境好出行方便地铁淘金站就在酒店旁边……', '2023-09-14', 5, '[''交通便利性'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235012000c4oez396486_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236y12000c4ohq1v3380_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '位置、环境俱佳，硬件无可挑剔。最令人无语的就是二楼的特色餐厅荔湾亭，价钱贵，完全', '位置、环境俱佳，硬件无可挑剔。最令人无语的就是二楼的特色餐厅荔湾亭，价钱贵，完全符合五星级收费标准，可惜出品比街边大排档还要低几个档次！现在的荔湾亭已经不是当年的荔湾亭了，连我这个地道广州人都感觉难以下咽！', '2023-06-16', 4, '[''餐饮设施'', ''价格合理性'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233812000bff3pn27AFB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235712000bff476p0963_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230n12000bff2dmz9F4E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235t12000bff4qod1E23_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233612000bff9c2tADA2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '房间很舒适，服务到位，遗漏的现金也通知我回去拿，非常满意', '房间很舒适，服务到位，遗漏的现金也通知我回去拿，非常满意', '2023-10-01', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236a12000caqc4yh17CB_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '客房免费升级为套房，酒店很安静，配套设施齐全，服务没话说，就是早餐人太多，要排队', '客房免费升级为套房，酒店很安静，配套设施齐全，服务没话说，就是早餐人太多，要排队', '2023-09-10', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''安静程度'', ''餐饮设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236512000c3og9nqD569_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232u12000c3oa7do3D35_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231712000c3oab0yAC4A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '环境非常好??', '环境非常好??', '2024-02-02', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0237312000d3tfn2m3C06_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230a12000d3tfjbg35A1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231412000d3tfkjbD1F4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店环境舒适，服务质量好。', '酒店环境舒适，服务质量好。', '2023-10-29', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'', ''客房服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236k12000ch0jf4190F1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235g12000ch0d69q3D54_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231212000ch0rc8yDD8E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '原来华为广州办事处也在这里，哈哈哈，大大的赞', '原来华为广州办事处也在这里，哈哈哈，大大的赞', '2023-10-07', 5, '[''周边配套'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231l12000cchvh9dB19B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '早餐品种丰富', '早餐品种丰富', '2023-11-15', 5, '[''餐饮设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233512000ckpabco345B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店年久老旧，卫生间淋浴高仪水龙头水管滋水，马桶非电动圈。客房?香味难闻 由于客', '酒店年久老旧，卫生间淋浴高仪水龙头水管滋水，马桶非电动圈。客房?香味难闻 由于客房数量众多，打扫慢。因位置入住率高。排队入住起码半小时以上。
还有个缺陷 是酒店附近再修地铁，（前台义正言辞说是政府工程）
客房非常受噪音的影响，建议携程预订时告知真实情况。
花园酒店对花园这边客房 要么不售卖 要么降价售卖 。而不是到酒店前台才告之 。广州酒店众多携程定1000+一晚上 因为噪音完全无法入睡。夜晚22:00见视频噪音
餐饮桃园馆 还不错。
昨日入住对面的友谊商店发生火灾，不宜停留。
这个价位还是去住珠江新城吧。', '2023-05-28', 2, '[''房间设施'', ''安静程度'', ''退房/入住效率'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0200h12000bb6zdojBC82_W_350_350_R5_Q70.jpg?proc=autoorient\", \"https://pages.c-ctrip.com/hotels/IBU/online/play-icon.png\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232612000bb6j8ql0C22_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231a12000bb6vf3q6CF4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232012000bb6siauDB53_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '广州花园酒店不愧是老牌高档酒店之一，拉满仪式感的入口门廊，气派的大堂，第一印象非', '广州花园酒店不愧是老牌高档酒店之一，拉满仪式感的入口门廊，气派的大堂，第一印象非常好。办理入住时赶上酒店举办活动，等的时间有点长，和客服沟通后，工作人员迅速调整工作，很快解决问题。体验了一下露天泳池，下午五点太阳不晒，水温很适合，早餐一层的瀑布餐厅和二层的酒吧式餐厅各有特色。入住两天，感觉酒店的工作人员非常和善有礼，留下美好回忆。', '2023-06-19', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'', ''公共设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235z12000bg7y4rpA2BD_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234012000bg81fkt601E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231v12000bg82t6rDC36_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235412000bg7xjfjB008_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231z12000bg83rw27266_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234j12000bg7x08t1BC9_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '强烈推荐这家酒店性价比高，无论旅游都是一个不错的选择。服务非常好。前台Kasas', '强烈推荐这家酒店性价比高，无论旅游都是一个不错的选择。服务非常好。前台Kasas 不错。   迎宾李文热情下次还会来继续住。', '2025-03-29', 5, '[''性价比'', ''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233k12000jejsqpn4FB6_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '干净